name: The Magician's Code: Part 2
writer: Carter Bays (creator), Craig Thomas (creator), Carter Bays, Craig Thomas, Craig Gerard (story editor), Matthew Zinman (story editor), Dan Gregor (story editor), Doug Mand (story editor)
actors: Josh Radnor, Jason Segel, Cobie Smulders, Neil Patrick Harris
plot: Ted makes a fateful phone call to his old girlfriend Victoria, Barney's magic trick gets him in trouble with airport security just as he's about to leave on a trip with Quinn, and Robin tries to take the perfect birth announcement photo.
